Eveready East Africa May Close Kenyan Manufacturing Plant, Daily Reports

-- B y   E r i c   O m b o k
-- 
2011-05-23T04:30:43Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-23/eveready-east-africa-may-close-kenyan-manufacturing-plant-daily-reports.html
Eveready East Africa Ltd. (EVRD)  is
considering shutting its Kenyan plant in a cost-cutting
initiative that may result in 170 employees losing their jobs,
Business Daily reported, citing newly appointed Managing
Director Jackson Mutua.  The company may outsource its manufacturing to nations with
lower operating costs, the Nairobi-based newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Eric Ombok in Nairobi at 
 eombok@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Victoria Batchelor at 
 vbatchelor@bloomberg.net  